, 50664], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.060943437345100174, "compression_ratio": 1.5151515151515151, "no_speech_prob": 0.028582477942109108}, {"id": 67, "seek": 31900, "start": 325.0, "end": 334.0, "text": " So that sounds to me as though he accepts the fact that I'm not going to pay and that the invoice has been waived.", "tokens": [50664, 407, 300, 3263, 281, 385, 382, 1673, 415, 33538, 264, 1186, 300, 286, 478, 406, 516, 281, 1689, 293, 300, 264, 47919, 575, 668, 5406, 3194, 13, 51114], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.060943437345100174, "compression_ratio": 1.5151515151515151, "no_speech_prob": 0.028582477942109108}, {"id": 68, "seek": 31900, "start": 334.0, "end": 340.0, "text": " If that's not the case, then that was not conveyed very well.", "tokens": [51114, 759, 300, 311, 406, 264, 1389, 11, 550, 300, 390, 406, 49340, 588, 731, 13, 51414], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.060943437345100174, "compression_ratio": 1.5151515151515151, "no_speech_prob": 0.028582477942109108}, {"id": 69, "seek": 34000, "start": 340.0, "end": 357.0, "text": " And that just goes to show that eco shield does not have very good communication skills with their customers, especially the ones that aren't happy with them to begin with.", "tokens": [50364, 400, 300, 445, 1709, 281, 855, 300, 30226, 10257, 775, 406, 362, 588, 665, 6101, 3942, 365, 641, 4581, 11, 2318, 264, 2306, 300, 3212, 380, 2055, 365, 552, 281, 1841, 365, 13, 51214], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11056557217159786, "compression_ratio": 1.3650793650793651, "no_speech_prob": 0.47835057973861694}, {"id": 70, "seek": 35700, "start": 357.0, "end": 367.0, "text": " I understand. So all your concerns will be noted. And also I already also saw a notation here from the local office wall regarding the cancellation.", "tokens": [50364, 286, 1223, 13, 407, 439, 428, 7389, 486, 312, 12964, 13, 400, 611, 286, 1217, 611, 1866, 257, 24657, 510, 490, 264, 2654, 3398, 2929, 8595, 264, 45867, 13, 50864], "temp